                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mt-4 text-justify">My first blog post</h1>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-8 text-gray-600 text-justify">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet,
                        consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras fringilla dignissim sagittis. Phasellus hendrerit diam a metus
